    • Constructor Detail

      • BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2

        public BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2()
        Create an object that holds a null BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2.
        The call isNull() on the object created will returns true.
          BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2 obj = new BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2();
  (obj == null) <=> false
  obj.isNull() <=> true
        To creates a new BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2, use the static "constructor" : 
          BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2 obj = BASS_BFX_COMPRESSOR2.allocate();
        See Also:
        allocate()
